      "creation_date" : 1267791501,
      "post_id" : 2383291,
      "comment_id" : 2364394,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
      "body" : "It&#39;s better to use standard library to handle byte -&gt; int conversions than to hand code. Java even provides a library for doing this with different endianess, see java.nio.ByteBuffer."
