      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Thanks for the code snippet, i should point out a bug here - <code>ret |= (int)bytes[i] &amp; 0xFF;</code> should really be <code>ret |= (int)bytes[i + offset] &amp; 0xFF;</code> - otherwise the offset param is ignored completely."
