      "body" : "It&#39;s not because of the &quot;faster&quot; code that you should use <code>&lt;&lt;</code>, it&#39;s because of readability. By using <code>&lt;&lt;</code>, it is clear that we are doing bit operations rather than multiplication. In fact, I&#39;d even change the <code>+</code>s to <code>|</code>s"
