      "comment_id" : 9011344,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It should be noted that this is for big-endian ordered bytes, where as support for little only takes a small change:  return ((ch4 &lt;&lt; 24) + (ch3 &lt;&lt; 16) + (ch2 &lt;&lt; 8) + (ch1 &lt;&lt; 0));"
