    "creation_date" : 1267786374,
    "answer_id" : 2386134,
    "question_id" : 2383265,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>See <a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/io/DataInputStream.html#readInt\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>DataInputStream.readInt</code></a>. Here is an example:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>int ch1 = in.read();\nint ch2 = in.read();\nint ch3 = in.read();\nint ch4 = in.read();\nif ((ch1 | ch2 | ch3 | ch4) &lt; 0)\n    throw new EOFException();\nreturn ((ch1 &lt;&lt; 24) + (ch2 &lt;&lt; 16) + (ch3 &lt;&lt; 8) + (ch4 &lt;&lt; 0));\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 127226,
      "reputation" : 8368,
      "user_id" : 324249,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 96,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/bd6682769f58076c2cdc6fea774e7826?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
